{
  "video_id": "zG21nyJNB_A",
  "title": "Sanjay Pradhan: How open data is changing international aid",
  "es": 1,
  "json": [
    {
      "index": 1,
      "start_time": 0.0,
      "end_time": 7000.0,
      "text": "Translator: Joseph Geni Reviewer: Morton Bast"
    },
    {
      "index": 2,
      "start_time": 15662.0,
      "end_time": 20671.0,
      "text": "I grew up in Bihar, India&#39;s poorest state,"
    },
    {
      "index": 3,
      "start_time": 20671.0,
      "end_time": 24137.0,
      "text": "and I remember when I was six years old,"
    },
    {
      "index": 4,
      "start_time": 24137.0,
      "end_time": 27903.0,
      "text": "I remember coming home one day to find a cart"
    },
    {
      "index": 5,
      "start_time": 27903.0,
      "end_time": 33224.0,
      "text": "full of the most delicious sweets at our doorstep."
    },
    {
      "index": 6,
      "start_time": 33224.0,
      "end_time": 36712.0,
      "text": "My brothers and I dug in,"
    },
    {
      "index": 7,
      "start_time": 36713.0,
      "end_time": 40100.0,
      "text": "and that&#39;s when my father came home."
    },
    {
      "index": 8,
      "start_time": 40100.0,
      "end_time": 45464.0,
      "text": "He was livid, and I still remember how we cried"
    },
    {
      "index": 9,
      "start_time": 45465.0,
      "end_time": 49529.0,
      "text": "when that cart with our half-eaten sweets"
    },
    {
      "index": 10,
      "start_time": 49529.0,
      "end_time": 52746.0,
      "text": "was pulled away from us."
    },
    {
      "index": 11,
      "start_time": 52746.0,
      "end_time": 57547.0,
      "text": "Later, I understood why my father got so upset."
    },
    {
      "index": 12,
      "start_time": 57547.0,
      "end_time": 60772.0,
      "text": "Those sweets were a bribe"
    },
    {
      "index": 13,
      "start_time": 60772.0,
      "end_time": 64352.0,
      "text": "from a contractor who was trying to get my father"
    },
    {
      "index": 14,
      "start_time": 64352.00000000001,
      "end_time": 67815.0,
      "text": "to award him a government contract."
    },
    {
      "index": 15,
      "start_time": 67816.0,
      "end_time": 72477.0,
      "text": "My father was responsible for building roads in Bihar,"
    },
    {
      "index": 16,
      "start_time": 72477.0,
      "end_time": 77800.0,
      "text": "and he had developed a firm stance against corruption,"
    },
    {
      "index": 17,
      "start_time": 77800.0,
      "end_time": 81128.0,
      "text": "even though he was harassed and threatened."
    },
    {
      "index": 18,
      "start_time": 81128.0,
      "end_time": 84496.0,
      "text": "His was a lonely struggle, because Bihar"
    },
    {
      "index": 19,
      "start_time": 84496.0,
      "end_time": 88232.0,
      "text": "was also India&#39;s most corrupt state,"
    },
    {
      "index": 20,
      "start_time": 88233.0,
      "end_time": 91995.0,
      "text": "where public officials were enriching themselves,"
    },
    {
      "index": 21,
      "start_time": 91995.0,
      "end_time": 96880.0,
      "text": "[rather] than serving the poor who had no means"
    },
    {
      "index": 22,
      "start_time": 96880.0,
      "end_time": 100330.0,
      "text": "to express their anguish if their children"
    },
    {
      "index": 23,
      "start_time": 100340.0,
      "end_time": 103867.0,
      "text": "had no food or no schooling."
    },
    {
      "index": 24,
      "start_time": 103867.0,
      "end_time": 108224.0,
      "text": "And I experienced this most viscerally"
    },
    {
      "index": 25,
      "start_time": 108224.0,
      "end_time": 114522.0,
      "text": "when I traveled to remote villages to study poverty."
    },
    {
      "index": 26,
      "start_time": 114522.0,
      "end_time": 118339.0,
      "text": "And as I went village to village,"
    },
    {
      "index": 27,
      "start_time": 118339.0,
      "end_time": 124851.0,
      "text": "I remember one day, when I was famished and exhausted,"
    },
    {
      "index": 28,
      "start_time": 124851.0,
      "end_time": 127170.0,
      "text": "and I was almost collapsing"
    },
    {
      "index": 29,
      "start_time": 127170.0,
      "end_time": 130199.0,
      "text": "in a scorching heat under a tree,"
    },
    {
      "index": 30,
      "start_time": 130199.00000000001,
      "end_time": 136259.0,
      "text": "and just at that time, one of the poorest men in that village"
    },
    {
      "index": 31,
      "start_time": 136259.0,
      "end_time": 142174.0,
      "text": "invited me into his hut and graciously fed me."
    },
    {
      "index": 32,
      "start_time": 142175.0,
      "end_time": 146823.0,
      "text": "Only I later realized that what he fed me"
    },
    {
      "index": 33,
      "start_time": 146823.0,
      "end_time": 152566.0,
      "text": "was food for his entire family for two days."
    },
    {
      "index": 34,
      "start_time": 152566.0,
      "end_time": 156989.0,
      "text": "This profound gift of generosity"
    },
    {
      "index": 35,
      "start_time": 156989.0,
      "end_time": 162267.0,
      "text": "challenged and changed the very purpose of my life."
    },
    {
      "index": 36,
      "start_time": 162267.0,
      "end_time": 166390.0,
      "text": "I resolved to give back."
    },
    {
      "index": 37,
      "start_time": 166390.0,
      "end_time": 170343.0,
      "text": "Later, I joined the World Bank, which sought to fight"
    },
    {
      "index": 38,
      "start_time": 170343.0,
      "end_time": 176111.0,
      "text": "such poverty by transferring aid from rich to poor countries."
    },
    {
      "index": 39,
      "start_time": 176111.0,
      "end_time": 181143.0,
      "text": "My initial work focused on Uganda, where I focused"
    },
    {
      "index": 40,
      "start_time": 181143.0,
      "end_time": 185371.0,
      "text": "on negotiating reforms with the Finance Ministry of Uganda"
    },
    {
      "index": 41,
      "start_time": 185371.0,
      "end_time": 188200.0,
      "text": "so they could access our loans."
    },
    {
      "index": 42,
      "start_time": 188200.0,
      "end_time": 191331.0,
      "text": "But after we disbursed the loans, I remember"
    },
    {
      "index": 43,
      "start_time": 191331.0,
      "end_time": 196480.0,
      "text": "a trip in Uganda where I found newly built schools"
    },
    {
      "index": 44,
      "start_time": 196490.0,
      "end_time": 198833.0,
      "text": "without textbooks or teachers,"
    },
    {
      "index": 45,
      "start_time": 198833.0,
      "end_time": 201753.0,
      "text": "new health clinics without drugs,"
    },
    {
      "index": 46,
      "start_time": 201753.0,
      "end_time": 207535.0,
      "text": "and the poor once again without any voice or recourse."
    },
    {
      "index": 47,
      "start_time": 207536.0,
      "end_time": 211112.0,
      "text": "It was Bihar all over again."
    },
    {
      "index": 48,
      "start_time": 211112.0,
      "end_time": 215720.0,
      "text": "Bihar represents the challenge of development:"
    },
    {
      "index": 49,
      "start_time": 215720.0,
      "end_time": 218983.0,
      "text": "abject poverty surrounded by corruption."
    },
    {
      "index": 50,
      "start_time": 218983.0,
      "end_time": 223243.0,
      "text": "Globally, 1.3 billion people live on less than"
    },
    {
      "index": 51,
      "start_time": 223243.0,
      "end_time": 227952.0,
      "text": "$1.25 a day, and the work I did in Uganda"
    },
    {
      "index": 52,
      "start_time": 227952.0,
      "end_time": 232883.0,
      "text": "represents the traditional approach to these problems"
    },
    {
      "index": 53,
      "start_time": 232883.0,
      "end_time": 237175.0,
      "text": "that has been practiced since 1944,"
    },
    {
      "index": 54,
      "start_time": 237175.0,
      "end_time": 242795.0,
      "text": "when winners of World War II, 500 founding fathers,"
    },
    {
      "index": 55,
      "start_time": 242795.0,
      "end_time": 246231.0,
      "text": "and one lonely founding mother,"
    },
    {
      "index": 56,
      "start_time": 246231.0,
      "end_time": 248658.0,
      "text": "gathered in New Hampshire, USA,"
    },
    {
      "index": 57,
      "start_time": 248658.0,
      "end_time": 251277.0,
      "text": "to establish the Bretton Woods institutions,"
    },
    {
      "index": 58,
      "start_time": 251277.0,
      "end_time": 253820.0,
      "text": "including the World Bank."
    },
    {
      "index": 59,
      "start_time": 253820.0,
      "end_time": 256382.0,
      "text": "And that traditional approach to development"
    },
    {
      "index": 60,
      "start_time": 256382.0,
      "end_time": 260317.0,
      "text": "had three key elements. First, transfer of resources"
    },
    {
      "index": 61,
      "start_time": 260317.0,
      "end_time": 262269.0,
      "text": "from rich countries in the North"
    },
    {
      "index": 62,
      "start_time": 262269.0,
      "end_time": 264766.0,
      "text": "to poorer countries in the South,"
    },
    {
      "index": 63,
      "start_time": 264766.0,
      "end_time": 267659.0,
      "text": "accompanied by reform prescriptions."
    },
    {
      "index": 64,
      "start_time": 267659.0,
      "end_time": 271224.0,
      "text": "Second, the development institutions that channeled"
    },
    {
      "index": 65,
      "start_time": 271225.0,
      "end_time": 275987.0,
      "text": "these transfers were opaque, with little transparency"
    },
    {
      "index": 66,
      "start_time": 275987.0,
      "end_time": 279787.0,
      "text": "of what they financed or what results they achieved."
    },
    {
      "index": 67,
      "start_time": 279787.0,
      "end_time": 283700.0,
      "text": "And third, the engagement in developing countries"
    },
    {
      "index": 68,
      "start_time": 283700.0,
      "end_time": 286982.0,
      "text": "was with a narrow set of government elites"
    },
    {
      "index": 69,
      "start_time": 286982.0,
      "end_time": 290296.0,
      "text": "with little interaction with the citizens, who are"
    },
    {
      "index": 70,
      "start_time": 290296.0,
      "end_time": 294581.0,
      "text": "the ultimate beneficiaries of development assistance."
    },
    {
      "index": 71,
      "start_time": 294581.0,
      "end_time": 298782.0,
      "text": "Today, each of these elements is opening up"
    },
    {
      "index": 72,
      "start_time": 298782.0,
      "end_time": 302142.0,
      "text": "due to dramatic changes in the global environment."
    },
    {
      "index": 73,
      "start_time": 302142.0,
      "end_time": 305837.0,
      "text": "Open knowledge, open aid, open governance,"
    },
    {
      "index": 74,
      "start_time": 305837.0,
      "end_time": 309582.0,
      "text": "and together, they represent three key shifts"
    },
    {
      "index": 75,
      "start_time": 309582.0,
      "end_time": 312352.0,
      "text": "that are transforming development"
    },
    {
      "index": 76,
      "start_time": 312352.0,
      "end_time": 316650.0,
      "text": "and that also hold greater hope for the problems"
    },
    {
      "index": 77,
      "start_time": 316650.0,
      "end_time": 320638.0,
      "text": "I witnessed in Uganda and in Bihar."
    },
    {
      "index": 78,
      "start_time": 320638.0,
      "end_time": 323604.0,
      "text": "The first key shift is open knowledge."
    },
    {
      "index": 79,
      "start_time": 323604.0,
      "end_time": 327164.0,
      "text": "You know, developing countries today will not simply"
    },
    {
      "index": 80,
      "start_time": 327165.0,
      "end_time": 330762.0,
      "text": "accept solutions that are handed down to them"
    },
    {
      "index": 81,
      "start_time": 330762.0,
      "end_time": 334389.0,
      "text": "by the U.S., Europe or the World Bank."
    },
    {
      "index": 82,
      "start_time": 334389.0,
      "end_time": 337224.0,
      "text": "They get their inspiration, their hope,"
    },
    {
      "index": 83,
      "start_time": 337224.0,
      "end_time": 339623.0,
      "text": "their practical know-how,"
    },
    {
      "index": 84,
      "start_time": 339624.0,
      "end_time": 343175.0,
      "text": "from successful emerging economies in the South."
    },
    {
      "index": 85,
      "start_time": 343175.0,
      "end_time": 347855.0,
      "text": "They want to know how China lifted 500 million people"
    },
    {
      "index": 86,
      "start_time": 347855.0,
      "end_time": 351518.0,
      "text": "out of poverty in 30 years,"
    },
    {
      "index": 87,
      "start_time": 351518.0,
      "end_time": 354464.0,
      "text": "how Mexico&#39;s Oportunidades program"
    },
    {
      "index": 88,
      "start_time": 354464.0,
      "end_time": 359160.0,
      "text": "improved schooling and nutrition for millions of children."
    },
    {
      "index": 89,
      "start_time": 359160.0,
      "end_time": 364822.0,
      "text": "This is the new ecosystem of open-knowledge flows,"
    },
    {
      "index": 90,
      "start_time": 364822.0,
      "end_time": 369755.0,
      "text": "not just traveling North to South, but South to South,"
    },
    {
      "index": 91,
      "start_time": 369755.0,
      "end_time": 372580.0,
      "text": "and even South to North,"
    },
    {
      "index": 92,
      "start_time": 372580.0,
      "end_time": 377800.0,
      "text": "with Mexico&#39;s Oportunidades today inspiring New York City."
    },
    {
      "index": 93,
      "start_time": 377800.0,
      "end_time": 381648.0,
      "text": "And just as these North-to-South transfers are opening up,"
    },
    {
      "index": 94,
      "start_time": 381648.0,
      "end_time": 384488.0,
      "text": "so too are the development institutions"
    },
    {
      "index": 95,
      "start_time": 384488.0,
      "end_time": 387150.0,
      "text": "that channeled these transfers."
    },
    {
      "index": 96,
      "start_time": 387150.0,
      "end_time": 390884.0,
      "text": "This is the second shift: open aid."
    },
    {
      "index": 97,
      "start_time": 390884.0,
      "end_time": 394434.0,
      "text": "Recently, the World Bank opened its vault of data"
    },
    {
      "index": 98,
      "start_time": 394434.0,
      "end_time": 399297.0,
      "text": "for public use, releasing 8,000 economic and social indicators"
    },
    {
      "index": 99,
      "start_time": 399297.0,
      "end_time": 403666.0,
      "text": "for 200 countries over 50 years,"
    },
    {
      "index": 100,
      "start_time": 403666.0,
      "end_time": 407644.0,
      "text": "and it launched a global competition to crowdsource"
    },
    {
      "index": 101,
      "start_time": 407644.0,
      "end_time": 411311.0,
      "text": "innovative apps using this data."
    },
    {
      "index": 102,
      "start_time": 411311.0,
      "end_time": 414484.0,
      "text": "Development institutions today are also opening"
    },
    {
      "index": 103,
      "start_time": 414484.0,
      "end_time": 418298.0,
      "text": "for public scrutiny the projects they finance."
    },
    {
      "index": 104,
      "start_time": 418298.0,
      "end_time": 422563.0,
      "text": "Take GeoMapping. In this map from Kenya,"
    },
    {
      "index": 105,
      "start_time": 422563.0,
      "end_time": 427282.0,
      "text": "the red dots show where all the schools financed by donors"
    },
    {
      "index": 106,
      "start_time": 427282.0,
      "end_time": 431274.0,
      "text": "are located, and the darker the shade of green,"
    },
    {
      "index": 107,
      "start_time": 431274.0,
      "end_time": 434634.0,
      "text": "the more the number of out-of-school children."
    },
    {
      "index": 108,
      "start_time": 434634.0,
      "end_time": 438770.0,
      "text": "So this simple mashup reveals that donors"
    },
    {
      "index": 109,
      "start_time": 438770.0,
      "end_time": 441746.0,
      "text": "have not financed any schools in the areas"
    },
    {
      "index": 110,
      "start_time": 441746.0,
      "end_time": 443854.0,
      "text": "with the most out-of-school children,"
    },
    {
      "index": 111,
      "start_time": 443854.0,
      "end_time": 447945.0,
      "text": "provoking new questions. Is development assistance"
    },
    {
      "index": 112,
      "start_time": 447946.0,
      "end_time": 452565.0,
      "text": "targeting those who most need our help?"
    },
    {
      "index": 113,
      "start_time": 452565.0,
      "end_time": 455467.0,
      "text": "In this manner, the World Bank has now GeoMapped"
    },
    {
      "index": 114,
      "start_time": 455467.0,
      "end_time": 460409.0,
      "text": "30,000 project activities in 143 countries,"
    },
    {
      "index": 115,
      "start_time": 460409.0,
      "end_time": 463585.0,
      "text": "and donors are using a common platform"
    },
    {
      "index": 116,
      "start_time": 463585.0,
      "end_time": 466530.0,
      "text": "to map all their projects."
    },
    {
      "index": 117,
      "start_time": 466530.0,
      "end_time": 471392.0,
      "text": "This is a tremendous leap forward in transparency"
    },
    {
      "index": 118,
      "start_time": 471392.0,
      "end_time": 474234.0,
      "text": "and accountability of aid."
    },
    {
      "index": 119,
      "start_time": 474234.0,
      "end_time": 477229.0,
      "text": "And this leads me to the third, and in my view,"
    },
    {
      "index": 120,
      "start_time": 477230.0,
      "end_time": 480562.0,
      "text": "the most significant shift in development:"
    },
    {
      "index": 121,
      "start_time": 480562.0,
      "end_time": 484777.0,
      "text": "open governance. Governments today are opening up"
    },
    {
      "index": 122,
      "start_time": 484777.0,
      "end_time": 488753.0,
      "text": "just as citizens are demanding voice and accountability."
    },
    {
      "index": 123,
      "start_time": 488754.0,
      "end_time": 492784.0,
      "text": "From the Arab Spring to the Anna Hazare movement in India,"
    },
    {
      "index": 124,
      "start_time": 492784.0,
      "end_time": 495518.0,
      "text": "using mobile phones and social media"
    },
    {
      "index": 125,
      "start_time": 495518.0,
      "end_time": 498131.0,
      "text": "not just for political accountability"
    },
    {
      "index": 126,
      "start_time": 498132.0,
      "end_time": 502277.0,
      "text": "but also for development accountability."
    },
    {
      "index": 127,
      "start_time": 502277.0,
      "end_time": 506748.0,
      "text": "Are governments delivering services to the citizens?"
    },
    {
      "index": 128,
      "start_time": 506749.0,
      "end_time": 510894.0,
      "text": "So for instance, several governments in Africa"
    },
    {
      "index": 129,
      "start_time": 510894.0,
      "end_time": 515918.0,
      "text": "and Eastern Europe are opening their budgets to the public."
    },
    {
      "index": 130,
      "start_time": 515918.0,
      "end_time": 519321.0,
      "text": "But, you know, there is a big difference between a budget"
    },
    {
      "index": 131,
      "start_time": 519321.0,
      "end_time": 523358.0,
      "text": "that&#39;s public and a budget that&#39;s accessible."
    },
    {
      "index": 132,
      "start_time": 523357.0,
      "end_time": 528277.0,
      "text": "This is a public budget. (Laughter)"
    },
    {
      "index": 133,
      "start_time": 528278.0,
      "end_time": 531383.0,
      "text": "And as you can see, it&#39;s not really accessible"
    },
    {
      "index": 134,
      "start_time": 531383.0,
      "end_time": 534102.0,
      "text": "or understandable to an ordinary citizen"
    },
    {
      "index": 135,
      "start_time": 534102.0,
      "end_time": 539100.0,
      "text": "that is trying to understand how the government is spending its resources."
    },
    {
      "index": 136,
      "start_time": 539100.0,
      "end_time": 543350.0,
      "text": "To tackle this problem, governments are using new tools"
    },
    {
      "index": 137,
      "start_time": 543350.0,
      "end_time": 547718.0,
      "text": "to visualize the budget so it&#39;s more understandable"
    },
    {
      "index": 138,
      "start_time": 547718.0,
      "end_time": 549918.0,
      "text": "to the public."
    },
    {
      "index": 139,
      "start_time": 549918.0,
      "end_time": 553852.0,
      "text": "In this map from Moldova, the green color shows"
    },
    {
      "index": 140,
      "start_time": 553852.0,
      "end_time": 557939.0,
      "text": "those districts that have low spending on schools"
    },
    {
      "index": 141,
      "start_time": 557940.0,
      "end_time": 560260.0,
      "text": "but good educational outcomes,"
    },
    {
      "index": 142,
      "start_time": 560260.0,
      "end_time": 563509.0,
      "text": "and the red color shows the opposite."
    },
    {
      "index": 143,
      "start_time": 563509.0,
      "end_time": 570360.0,
      "text": "Tools like this help turn a shelf full of inscrutable documents"
    },
    {
      "index": 144,
      "start_time": 570360.0,
      "end_time": 573790.0,
      "text": "into a publicly understandable visual,"
    },
    {
      "index": 145,
      "start_time": 573790.0,
      "end_time": 577555.0,
      "text": "and what&#39;s exciting is that with this openness,"
    },
    {
      "index": 146,
      "start_time": 577556.0,
      "end_time": 581414.0,
      "text": "there are today new opportunities for citizens"
    },
    {
      "index": 147,
      "start_time": 581414.0,
      "end_time": 584939.0,
      "text": "to give feedback and engage with government."
    },
    {
      "index": 148,
      "start_time": 584940.0,
      "end_time": 589323.0,
      "text": "So in the Philippines today, parents and students"
    },
    {
      "index": 149,
      "start_time": 589323.0,
      "end_time": 593470.0,
      "text": "can give real-time feedback on a website,"
    },
    {
      "index": 150,
      "start_time": 593470.0,
      "end_time": 598562.0,
      "text": "Checkmyschool.org, or using SMS, whether teachers"
    },
    {
      "index": 151,
      "start_time": 598562.0,
      "end_time": 601356.0,
      "text": "and textbooks are showing up in school,"
    },
    {
      "index": 152,
      "start_time": 601356.0,
      "end_time": 606700.0,
      "text": "the same problems I witnessed in Uganda and in Bihar."
    },
    {
      "index": 153,
      "start_time": 606700.0,
      "end_time": 608858.0,
      "text": "And the government is responsive. So for instance,"
    },
    {
      "index": 154,
      "start_time": 608859.0,
      "end_time": 613369.0,
      "text": "when it was reported on this website that 800 students"
    },
    {
      "index": 155,
      "start_time": 613369.0,
      "end_time": 617555.0,
      "text": "were at risk because school repairs had stalled"
    },
    {
      "index": 156,
      "start_time": 617555.0,
      "end_time": 620146.0,
      "text": "due to corruption, the Department of Education"
    },
    {
      "index": 157,
      "start_time": 620146.0,
      "end_time": 623990.0,
      "text": "in the Philippines took swift action."
    },
    {
      "index": 158,
      "start_time": 623100.0,
      "end_time": 626797.0,
      "text": "And you know what&#39;s exciting is that this innovation"
    },
    {
      "index": 159,
      "start_time": 626797.0,
      "end_time": 631459.0,
      "text": "is now spreading South to South, from the Philippines"
    },
    {
      "index": 160,
      "start_time": 631459.0,
      "end_time": 635804.0,
      "text": "to Indonesia, Kenya, Moldova and beyond."
    },
    {
      "index": 161,
      "start_time": 635804.0,
      "end_time": 640630.0,
      "text": "In Dar es Salaam, Tanzania, even an impoverished"
    },
    {
      "index": 162,
      "start_time": 640630.0,
      "end_time": 643617.0,
      "text": "community was able to use these tools"
    },
    {
      "index": 163,
      "start_time": 643617.0,
      "end_time": 646589.0,
      "text": "to voice its aspirations."
    },
    {
      "index": 164,
      "start_time": 646589.0,
      "end_time": 649508.0,
      "text": "This is what the map of Tandale looked like"
    },
    {
      "index": 165,
      "start_time": 649508.0,
      "end_time": 653861.0,
      "text": "in August, 2011. But within a few weeks,"
    },
    {
      "index": 166,
      "start_time": 653861.0,
      "end_time": 658327.0,
      "text": "university students were able to use mobile phones"
    },
    {
      "index": 167,
      "start_time": 658327.0,
      "end_time": 662877.0,
      "text": "and an open-source platform to dramatically map"
    },
    {
      "index": 168,
      "start_time": 662877.0,
      "end_time": 666363.0,
      "text": "the entire community infrastructure."
    },
    {
      "index": 169,
      "start_time": 666364.0,
      "end_time": 670829.0,
      "text": "And what is very exciting is that citizens were then"
    },
    {
      "index": 170,
      "start_time": 670829.0,
      "end_time": 675835.0,
      "text": "able to give feedback as to which health or water points"
    },
    {
      "index": 171,
      "start_time": 675836.0,
      "end_time": 678710.0,
      "text": "were not working, aggregated"
    },
    {
      "index": 172,
      "start_time": 678710.0,
      "end_time": 681310.0,
      "text": "in the red bubbles that you see,"
    },
    {
      "index": 173,
      "start_time": 681310.0,
      "end_time": 685907.0,
      "text": "which together provides a graphic visual"
    },
    {
      "index": 174,
      "start_time": 685908.0,
      "end_time": 690363.0,
      "text": "of the collective voices of the poor."
    },
    {
      "index": 175,
      "start_time": 690363.0,
      "end_time": 695973.0,
      "text": "Today, even Bihar is turning around and opening up"
    },
    {
      "index": 176,
      "start_time": 695973.0,
      "end_time": 698844.0,
      "text": "under a committed leadership that is making government"
    },
    {
      "index": 177,
      "start_time": 698845.0,
      "end_time": 704130.0,
      "text": "transparent, accessible and responsive to the poor."
    },
    {
      "index": 178,
      "start_time": 704130.0,
      "end_time": 707541.0,
      "text": "But, you know, in many parts of the world,"
    },
    {
      "index": 179,
      "start_time": 707541.0,
      "end_time": 710519.0,
      "text": "governments are not interested in opening up"
    },
    {
      "index": 180,
      "start_time": 710519.0,
      "end_time": 715636.0,
      "text": "or in serving the poor, and it is a real challenge"
    },
    {
      "index": 181,
      "start_time": 715636.0,
      "end_time": 719980.0,
      "text": "for those who want to change the system."
    },
    {
      "index": 182,
      "start_time": 719980.0,
      "end_time": 723549.0,
      "text": "These are the lonely warriors"
    },
    {
      "index": 183,
      "start_time": 723549.0,
      "end_time": 727130.0,
      "text": "like my father and many, many others,"
    },
    {
      "index": 184,
      "start_time": 727130.0,
      "end_time": 730137.0,
      "text": "and a key frontier of development work"
    },
    {
      "index": 185,
      "start_time": 730137.0,
      "end_time": 735333.0,
      "text": "is to help these lonely warriors join hands"
    },
    {
      "index": 186,
      "start_time": 735333.0,
      "end_time": 738874.0,
      "text": "so they can together overcome the odds."
    },
    {
      "index": 187,
      "start_time": 738874.0,
      "end_time": 743617.0,
      "text": "So for instance, today, in Ghana, courageous reformers"
    },
    {
      "index": 188,
      "start_time": 743617.0,
      "end_time": 746817.0,
      "text": "from civil society, Parliament and government,"
    },
    {
      "index": 189,
      "start_time": 746817.0,
      "end_time": 751900.0,
      "text": "have forged a coalition for transparent contracts"
    },
    {
      "index": 190,
      "start_time": 751900.0,
      "end_time": 755650.0,
      "text": "in the oil sector, and, galvanized by this,"
    },
    {
      "index": 191,
      "start_time": 755650.0,
      "end_time": 760745.0,
      "text": "reformers in Parliament are now investigating dubious contracts."
    },
    {
      "index": 192,
      "start_time": 760745.0,
      "end_time": 765673.0,
      "text": "These examples give new hope, new possibility"
    },
    {
      "index": 193,
      "start_time": 765673.0,
      "end_time": 768785.0,
      "text": "to the problems I witnessed in Uganda"
    },
    {
      "index": 194,
      "start_time": 768785.0,
      "end_time": 773887.0,
      "text": "or that my father confronted in Bihar."
    },
    {
      "index": 195,
      "start_time": 773887.0,
      "end_time": 780856.0,
      "text": "Two years ago, on April 8th, 2010, I called my father."
    },
    {
      "index": 196,
      "start_time": 780856.0,
      "end_time": 786254.0,
      "text": "It was very late at night, and at age 80,"
    },
    {
      "index": 197,
      "start_time": 786254.0,
      "end_time": 791550.0,
      "text": "he was typing a 70-page public interest litigation"
    },
    {
      "index": 198,
      "start_time": 791550.0,
      "end_time": 794669.0,
      "text": "against corruption in a road project."
    },
    {
      "index": 199,
      "start_time": 794669.0,
      "end_time": 799287.0,
      "text": "Though he was no lawyer, he argued the case in court"
    },
    {
      "index": 200,
      "start_time": 799287.0,
      "end_time": 803501.0,
      "text": "himself the next day. He won the ruling,"
    },
    {
      "index": 201,
      "start_time": 803501.0,
      "end_time": 805523.0,
      "text": "but later that very evening,"
    },
    {
      "index": 202,
      "start_time": 805523.0,
      "end_time": 810117.0,
      "text": "he fell, and he died."
    },
    {
      "index": 203,
      "start_time": 810117.0,
      "end_time": 815600.0,
      "text": "He fought till the end, increasingly passionate"
    },
    {
      "index": 204,
      "start_time": 815610.0,
      "end_time": 819600.0,
      "text": "that to combat corruption and poverty,"
    },
    {
      "index": 205,
      "start_time": 819600.0,
      "end_time": 823120.0,
      "text": "not only did government officials need to be honest,"
    },
    {
      "index": 206,
      "start_time": 823130.0,
      "end_time": 826262.0,
      "text": "but citizens needed to join together"
    },
    {
      "index": 207,
      "start_time": 826262.0,
      "end_time": 829156.0,
      "text": "to make their voices heard."
    },
    {
      "index": 208,
      "start_time": 829157.0,
      "end_time": 834180.0,
      "text": "These became the two bookends of his life,"
    },
    {
      "index": 209,
      "start_time": 834180.0,
      "end_time": 836732.0,
      "text": "and the journey he traveled in between"
    },
    {
      "index": 210,
      "start_time": 836732.0,
      "end_time": 841516.0,
      "text": "mirrored the changing development landscape."
    },
    {
      "index": 211,
      "start_time": 841517.0,
      "end_time": 846470.0,
      "text": "Today, I&#39;m inspired by these changes, and I&#39;m excited"
    },
    {
      "index": 212,
      "start_time": 846470.0,
      "end_time": 849574.0,
      "text": "that at the World Bank, we are embracing"
    },
    {
      "index": 213,
      "start_time": 849574.0,
      "end_time": 852663.0,
      "text": "these new directions, a significant departure"
    },
    {
      "index": 214,
      "start_time": 852663.0,
      "end_time": 856541.0,
      "text": "from my work in Uganda 20 years ago."
    },
    {
      "index": 215,
      "start_time": 856541.0,
      "end_time": 860820.0,
      "text": "We need to radically open up development"
    },
    {
      "index": 216,
      "start_time": 860820.0,
      "end_time": 862886.0,
      "text": "so knowledge flows in multiple directions,"
    },
    {
      "index": 217,
      "start_time": 862886.0,
      "end_time": 867677.0,
      "text": "inspiring practitioners, so aid becomes transparent,"
    },
    {
      "index": 218,
      "start_time": 867677.0,
      "end_time": 871836.0,
      "text": "accountable and effective, so governments open up"
    },
    {
      "index": 219,
      "start_time": 871836.0,
      "end_time": 875782.0,
      "text": "and citizens are engaged and empowered"
    },
    {
      "index": 220,
      "start_time": 875782.0,
      "end_time": 877441.0,
      "text": "with reformers in government."
    },
    {
      "index": 221,
      "start_time": 877441.0,
      "end_time": 880638.0,
      "text": "We need to accelerate these shifts."
    },
    {
      "index": 222,
      "start_time": 880638.0,
      "end_time": 885638.0,
      "text": "If we do, we will find that the collective voices"
    },
    {
      "index": 223,
      "start_time": 885638.0,
      "end_time": 890280.0,
      "text": "of the poor will be heard in Bihar,"
    },
    {
      "index": 224,
      "start_time": 890280.0,
      "end_time": 892250.0,
      "text": "in Uganda, and beyond."
    },
    {
      "index": 225,
      "start_time": 892250.0,
      "end_time": 896325.0,
      "text": "We will find that textbooks and teachers"
    },
    {
      "index": 226,
      "start_time": 896325.0,
      "end_time": 899362.0,
      "text": "will show up in schools for their children."
    },
    {
      "index": 227,
      "start_time": 899362.0,
      "end_time": 903444.0,
      "text": "We will find that these children, too,"
    },
    {
      "index": 228,
      "start_time": 903445.0,
      "end_time": 909563.0,
      "text": "have a real chance of breaking their way out of poverty."
    },
    {
      "index": 229,
      "start_time": 909563.0,
      "end_time": 912778.0,
      "text": "Thank you. (Applause)"
    },
    {
      "index": 230,
      "start_time": 912778.0,
      "end_time": 915498.0,
      "text": "(Applause)"
    }
  ]
}